The '''priest-princes''' were the rulers of [[Monor II]]. The Agapos line ruled consecutively during the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]]; members included [[Agapos the Eighth]], [[Agapos the Ninth|Ninth]], and [[Agapos the Tenth|Tenth]].

